WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.500
Birds are amazing creatures of the sky.

00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:05.000
They soar high, singing beautiful songs.

00:00:05.100 --> 00:00:07.800
Different species have colorful feathers.

00:00:07.900 --> 00:00:10.000
Birds travel long distances during migration.

00:00:10.100 --> 00:00:11.000
They bring joy to nature lovers everywhere.
